Dude i dont know anymore...   I like Jess, even though her and alex just broke up.  Thats cool she told Matt that she liked me and whatever.. And that she could see herself going out with me but i guess she changed her mind, or maybe becasue i was there for her right after Cosner that maybe i was just a rebound...        But thats cool, Anywho even though she totally lead me on, She likes one of my very good friends Zach....  Only problem is he doesnt like her casue hes currently talking to someone else. But you know what Zach is a good guy and he does deserve happiness above anyone else i know.  Even above me..  Not like Jess liked me anyway i dont know why i cared so much about her...  I mean jesus christ...  she beats me up all the time, calls me names, destorys what little self-confidnece i did have...  

So on top of being destoyred psyhcially and mentally, i was a rebound.  Dude i feel great. And i told the only girl who actully liked me, Emily to leave me alone so i could be alone in peace with Jess...


LOL i knew this shit would happen, it always does....   Im never liked, im always the guy they can run to knowing full on i dont want anything in exchange for helping them pick up the peices when some asshole rippes them aprt...      i just dont get why they keep going after assholes knowing that they could have me in a heart beat.....

Ya know, i had like a whole page written telling you guys about my life since me and matt were done fighting and when i tryed posting an image in here to show you guys my background, i closed out of that whole page...    So ill just do it another time, casue im pissed

Well ,its been foreversince the last update...    So here we go, Matt and Monica do infact go out and im totally ok with it casue like i told you, Matts a happy man! Theyve been going out for a while since i think it was 5/5/05..   :) Kinda hard to forget

   But today me and him got into a fight, casue i was talking about the new Jet Li movie in lunch today and He sat there and listened to me go on and on about it..  Then when Eric broke in and was like "I hate it when people ruin the movie for other people by TELLING THEM" i was like, ok ill stop thats cool...   But then matt went on about how he hated me telling him the movie...  and he always tells me to stop but i keep going on about it...   Well, he sat there at the lunch table and was listening to me until Eric said something...   and all sunday he didnt say a word either...  so i dont fuckin get it...  So i got pissed off, just closed my mouth...    And matt kept on asking me what was wrong, why i was pissed off, and when id go to say something hed start up a new sentence...   So i couldnt get a word out to explain why i was angry, so i exploded...  He just grabbed his books and left..  And hasnt spoken to me since..   Thats cool, its his right to be pissed, but it is also my right to be pissed too, that shit gets annyoing.. I mean it was ok i was giving away the movie, but to go on and on about how stuipd i was for doing that, and how many times he told me to shut up, and making me feel so small, and acutlly hurting my feelings...  I coudlnt take it, so i exploloed...  and i dont care if he ever talks to me again..  casue i dont need someone to hurt me all the time... 


Anyway, me and Emily Radcliff go out now, and i see a long term relationship finally, ive gone through so many girls that didnt last this long, and i think theres something here, Ive got invest in this... 


Everything else is fine...

In like 2 days its amazing how feelings can change...  I thought i liked Monica, but it turns out i like someone else...  But i cant say who cause im not sure if she wants me reaveling her until we go out or even if we go out... So its just safer this way...  

Havent seen monica since my birthday...  Havent spoken with her since then either...  Im sure matt has, but she didnt see it fit to call me so why should i call her? =) This other girl makes me very happy... And im sure that if we are to go out thatd we'd make a great couple becasue right now, i cant stand being away from her... But is ok casue i dont know wuts going on..

Matts fine, im fine, Alex is fine, Ryan is fine...   EVERYONE is ok....  :)  

Well alrighty guys im half asleep alrdy so ill get going like right now....

Later

Not much has been going on... I turn 16 tommorw at 10:12am  :)  Not gonna be in school casue its my fuckin birthday matts coming over and so is liz hopefully and were gonna watch movies :)   

Monica, ... ...   I really do not think she likes me... Matt swears she does, but when im in the same room as her i get this feeling that the ony reason she puts up with me coming over is becasue she likes matt...  And it isnt a problem that she likes matt over me casue that means hes gonna be a happy man! But i mean. why'd she have to lead me on? Just tell me from the begging that she didnt like me,maybe im just reading everything wrong and she does like me its just i cant see it....  Which i dont think is the case...  But she did just break up with chuck...    But then why would she flirt shamlessly infront of me with matt?   The only reason is becasie she likes him and shes useing me as a reason to talk with him?   Or im just being stuipd...

Poor Trish :( Eric and her anret talking anymore... Shes pretty upset about it but more angry then upset... Cause shes mad she lost someone imporant to her...  But she said her decion is to not tlak to eric and thats wut shes gonna stick too i guess....

Alex Cosnar told me that from his stand point that he thinks she likes me its just that i like her too much and i cant see it...  But i doubt thats true casue i dont care if she likes me now, It just dosent matter anymore...  Casue i dont care! I like someone else now and if shes got the sudden feeling that she lieks me i dont want to know aobut it... Casue she had ALOT of time to like me and go out with me but she didnt want too, she wanted to flirt with matt right in front of me.. Thats cool... Oh well, if she wants to be friends thats cool...

Goodnight guys

My weekend was good. Friday i had Mikey Bell and Alex Cosner over my house for Airsoft but it ended up not happening becasue we didnt have enough guns after Paul got there...  So we just sat around and talked about theories of our Universe and Paul spoke to jade for me, Now shes over me in a matter of 3 and a half seconds..  Which isnt bad, Its just that now i feel very alone.. And it doesnt help when the girl i like doesnt like me or cant show she does casue shes alrdy got a boyfriend...So i like a girl that alrdy has a man, which in-itself is werid..  But i like her alot and have liked her for a long time..

Saturday, Monica called me out of the blue and asked if me and Matt could go over to her house... Well i alrdy had Alex and Mikey over so i said to her that i had to wait for mikey and alex to leave then me and matt would be over..   I found out later on after matt had got off the phone with her.. That she said there were two reasons for her wanting us to come over.. 1. Was that she wanted Matt and Emma to start talking again, and Matt really didnt want to so it was a battle to even get him to go over there... and 2.Monica apprently said ( Now i dont and still do not belive this was said but Matt swears that it was) that she wanted to see me...  :)! But i doubt it was really said...   And even if it was i think that maybe she didnt even really mean me... She prolly meant Matt anyway.. Casue come on whod like me... ?  Other than Liz and Jade and Kelsey.. I got no one...   not even Jade anymore, But thats not a probelm...


Then Today i was soppsed to go to Monicas game... Me and Matt were gonig to her game to make her happy casue her boyfriend now doesnt even go over her house on the weekends...  So her game was 16 min. ago. So maybe now im going tover to Mollys house and hang out with Sarah and Moly and Liz and Caleb..  :)  Sounds like a good time in the making :)

Later guys
Matt

And leaving me to reset everything...   Then my norton anti-virus wouldnt turn back on, and my zonealarm was all kinds of fucked up casue of you turning off my transformer and crashing my shit...   So yea, i  was a little pissed...  Doesnt mean im stephen... I could be a bitch about it and be like "YO WHY YOU TYPEING SHIT ABOUT ME YO" But i wont casue im not stephen...  Just stop typeing shit about me...    If youve got a problem just try to come talk to me...    rather then bitching about it in the livejournal commuinty....   Id rather you tell me you got a problem with me then go tell all your friends first then come to me...   

Seems better that way...   Dont you think fag?   :)

Love you Danny,

Im feeling depressed....   For one, Jade will not get over, she is like refusing the urge to get over me... It hurts her less to just get over me casue im not looking for a girlfriend...  But just becasue im not looking for a girlfrien doesnt mean i cant have crushs does it? Casue i definlty have like 2 crushs...

But anyway... Today i was in wellness walking and Danielle and Christina are talking about Ron, Chrissy's ex and i was in front of them all...  So i was walking along with my headphones in and im just midning my own bee's wax when dani hits my hair..  :) Im like "Wth..." so i turn around and all i see is her amazing smile... And she points over to Chrissy.. LoL So i turn back around and take off my headphones.. So we start talking about Ron and how guys are dicks... I defened us good guys like Corey,Matt and myself TOOTH AND NAIL!!  But they are convinced that every guy in the world is a dick in their own special way...  

But as we were walking i started to walk with my head down to listen better, and consitrate more on the converstaion... So im sitting there listening to wut happened to dani and her ex boyfriend, and i alrdy know wut happened with chrissy and ron.. So im sitting here soaking up wut happend. He cheated on her, and thought she wouldnt notice... And a whole bunch more stuff and shize like that..  But...  Then she told chrissy something that really hurt me and made me very depressed........    She was like "Im not looking for anyone in this school, they're all immature, im going older, the only guy i like was a GI that got shipped out..." Im like...  "Why would she say that around me....."  oh yea thats right IM A PUSSY AND NEVER TOLD HER I HAD A CRUSH ON HER!!!!  

So i turn on my CD player and put my headphones on, Then calmy started speeding up and later on i got really far ahead on them...  And then i started to think about it... And i ran some situations through mey head and i came out with, If i got her my number and she started to come over shed change her mind about every guy in this school is immature... But i couldnt just do that out of the blue, so i ran the situation of doing it through scool in my head...  and that came out with her laughing at me bacially and crushing everything i had for her... Basically she was like "Hunny i think im a little to old for you... Go find someone your own age..."  And that hurts even thinkg about it.. So im not risking anything ill just get over it silently and be her friend if she still wants to talk to me..

And to top those things off, I still like Monica! WHICH isnt good casue shes got a boyfriend, but its cool casue i know she wouldnt cheat on him and i know she doesnt like me.. Which makes me 0 for 2.. Self Esteem on a scale of 1 to 10 is a resounding -65218414564854848   ....

The only people who are there for me to vent are people who like me.. Ive never vented to a guy for appernt reasons and only vented to 2 girls and both of which like me... Liz and Kelsey...  But then theres leesa and shes been there when ive vented but i never really put it all on her like i did Kelsey or Liz...

Justins a lucky guy

I need to a girl in mind and go after her...  Im tired of worrying if im steping on someone foot...  I really am...  I liked 2 girls and both of which do not like me...  Maybe i should go for this one in mind, if i work alot harder on her maybe shell like me, and she lives near me too!!  OOO  Maybe i should do that...  

"Should i put up my shining armor?
And put on the pimp shoes?
Or should i keep on the armor, just to kill the glow"
-Me   


Later,
Matt

Im glad no one took my test....    DICKS!!!  But its cool i guess...   Anyway, not much has happened over my spring break....

The first couple of days we were off Matt spent the night, and we played Onimusha 3, Demon Seige or however you spell it....  Then on Friday he went to work so i was home alone, and monica out of the blue IM'ed me... She was like "Hey, Matt told me to IM you, so wuts up" and i was like "Oh alright well i guess he wanted to know if we could come over..." and then it went from there, I think we went over he house twice over spring break...   But both times it was fun..  :)  And then me and Liz made up, and weve been talking again...  Alot....  I never quite got how cool it was talking to her again...  I mean i know i liked it before, But i mean i didnt know i missed it until i got it back...   Its cool....  :)  But today at like 630 monica was like "you guys should come to my game at 8"  and i had to go home and do some stuff and make sure it was cool with my mom and shit, but then when monica called me and i didnt have an answer to if i could come to the game yet so i told i couldnt.... But i definelty could and that kinda pissed me off.... 

So...  No airsoft or anything... Only a few girls that spoke to me...   I wish that Monica liked me.. At all....   But i mean if she doesnt then all i can just stay around till she likes me...

Calm, serene, and understanding, you make a worthy friend and a valuble ally to people in need. Don't change your sweet nature, your constant being-there can save a life. 
I suggest your go into a field that centers around working with others such as a doctor, baby-sitter, psychologist, lifeguard, or Teacher. If none of these occupations interest you, it is okay then. I am sure that there are plenty of oppertunities out there for you.

Well...  Its been a while...  Yesterday was Jayme's birthday party.. But it wasnt so much a party rather than a get-together... There were like 6 people there, Krista her little sister and her boyfriend, Vince, my old bestfriend, then Me and Matt, and Heather, Jayme's bestfriend...  Everything was going good...  The way i remeber it Heather was a bitch but when i got into the car she was really nice.. So i made alot of jokes and was being cool and so was Matt we were being oursleves... Everyone was having a great time...  Then we got home and everyone was having a good time, until Heather let it get to her that her boyfriend wasnt calling her...  So when she left Jayme's room and went into the basement, i had to make sure she was alright casue matt and jayme didnt want too...  So i went downstairs to see wut was wrong..  I sat on the bottom 2 steps and she sat on the...  ummm.... how do you spell this fuckin word.. foo-ton..  dunno or care..  so i cleared my throat and she said "I know your there, im not stuipd" and i said "No one said you were stuipd.." So then she looked over at the stairs and said..  "I like how my best friend came with you.." and i said "she didnt.." and she said "I know i was being sarcastic" Everyone knows i can take a joke and she didnt mean it to be sarcasticly funny, she was hinting on me to leave her alone...  So i sat there and exmanied the sitaution..  I came downstairs to help someone with a problem, someone i thought to be my friend, and she either didnt want my help or she just didnt like me enough as a friend to even think to talk to me.. Both of which hurt... So i just sat up after the examniation was down and said "oh, well then ill go get her for you..." and she said something along the lines of "I dont want to talk to her.." But i just kept on walking... The whole rest of the day i was upset towards Heather...  She kept on being moody and i just kept on getting hurt whenever i would get over it and try to help her again...  Like the one time me and Vince were playing pool and we were laughing and having a great time... I went over and threw some streamer on heather and my myself, and she just took it off and tore it up and kept playing super nintendo....  i try to cheer her up and she gets mad and doesnt want to have fun... So we leave to go to Krista's lacross game, me and Matt go to see my old neigborhood and Jayme and Heather go inside to the game, me and Matt are having fun seeing some of my old friends.. We got into the car with Heather and Jayme and shes pissed again...  So when we get home me and Heather get into a fight casue she told me not to be sarcastic...   LoL, First off never tell me to do anything unless i hold you at some kind of respect.. second never tell me NOT to be sarcastic and expect me to listen, i cant not be sarcastic, and if u jump ill lay down... So i told her to shut the fuck up, i just had it with her, "SHUT THE FUCK UP!"
So she stormed out and came back in the kitchen and threathen to beat my ass...  This is the same girl i had across my back and threw onto a couch.. She weights like 40 pounds but shes gonna fuckin slap the shit out of me...  So i was like "OH YEA!? WELL, ILL SHAKE THE SHIT RIGHT OUT OF YOU, BITCH!" She didnt like that very much..  so other than Heather, the get-together was a good time, i liked it...

But i feel bad at the same time casue i only made things worse for her, plus she drove us down there and she set up the party for jayme... So i was going to have jayme say sry to her but i didnt get to becasue i was too pissed off at her to even relay that message... Then as were about to leave i realize something... My jacket is in her trunk along with matts irish hat and and his name tag for work...  Shit...


But anyway about things up here, Me and Liz broke up like i think a week ago, tuesday, Me and her are talking though were on good speaking terms, and me and Jade are talking again, i think she likes me still.. it might be just a hunch but i think its right...  But, i dont know if i am going back out with her cause if i cheated on her one time wuts to say i wouldnt do it again, and i know its a thing of self-control.. And for you people who me, id rather not risk it if i think something like that might happen again, some might say thats bullshit, but i just dont trust myself yet...

I think i might have new crush, But i dont think i should just yet casue alot of girls who still like me read this, and they might say something to that girl that woudl ruin it... So ill leave her name as HER, For anyone of my guy friend just ask me and ill let you know her name..  But she is really cool, i spoekn with her like 3 times, and it was all peroid long...  I lent her my hoodie one class peroid and i was freezing my ass off talking with her, but i couldnt let her know that so i just kinda walk alongside of her saying "Uh huh, yea"  But shes really cool, and i think i do have a crush on her cause i look forward to seeing her and talking to her... Shes making me like school all over again...  LoL

My grades werent all that fucked up, i think im doing good but i need to bring up my World History grade... And keep all the rest up...  

"I trust this unconditionally, it tightens the knot in my stomach, it is truely beautiful in my eyes. I am falling in love with the unknown"-Unknowen

-Matt
